{"tid":951360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[racist] 喺食物落毒害黑人室友 留美華生被控企圖謀殺","createTime":"2018-12-22T09:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T10:16:55.000Z","uid":82917,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"be00949955223fc1c97e1029bfd429a907902457","tid":951360,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/172748_d22511c845f9ec8aa08f1a068723b8bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F172748_d22511c845f9ec8aa08f1a068723b8bc.png&h=aa4ec38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國一名中國留學生，連續多月在學校宿舍黑人室友的食物飲料中落毒，將被控企圖謀殺。<br />\n<br />\n22歲的楊宇凱（YuKai Yang，音）在賓夕凡尼亞州利哈伊大學（Lehigh University）主修化學，與同學羅亞爾（Juwan Royal）同房多年，羅亞爾一直當楊宇凱是老友，豈料楊宇凱今年春天開始，一連多月在羅亞爾食物、飲料、漱口水中摻入有劇毒的重金屬鉈（thallium）。羅亞爾漸漸出現暈眩、顫抖、嘔吐等徵狀。醫生為他驗血，發現他中鉈毒。當局表示，現已畢業的羅亞爾仍持續出現中毒徵狀。<br />\n<br />\n楊宇凱正被拘留，已被利哈伊大學開除學籍，學生簽證亦已被撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n另外，楊宇凱涉嫌在宿舍房內塗寫種族歧視字句，面臨種族恐嚇控罪。<br />\n<br />\n北安普敦縣檢察官表示，羅亞爾得知楊宇凱毒害他後大感詫異，因為他與對方同房多年，一直以為與對方相處融洽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181221/59053868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F59053868&d=cm2aClcYNw%2Fqjlfy3CxUbb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=8934a0e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F59053868&h=0ec176da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181221/59053868</a>"},{"pid":"42bc3cbe90ef4f83eb1348a77b9c1ae8c0b0e5e9","tid":951360,"uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:29:16.000Z","msg":"支那同黑人都係性格好cheap"},{"pid":"bd4e80936d20a3390327bb00e22baac8e3935adb","tid":951360,"uid":6842,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-2